Aim:- To print a pattern using loop statement by using shell scripting commands.
Algorithm:- 1) Read the number given. 2) Initialize the for loop where i<=$n. 3) Initiallize 
one more loop inside the above loop with j<=$i. 4) Print “*” and close the two loops. 5) 
Continue until the required root loops(rows) reached.
Program:-
number=1
echo”Enter number of rows”
read rows
for((i=1; i<=rows; i++))
do
 for((j=1; j<=i; j++))
 do
 echo -n "$number "
 number=$((number + 1))
 done
 number=1
 echo
done
